            <p class="text-justify">If you booked your <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/">flight tickets</a> using Air Canada's official website or a third-party website or an agent, you can only cancel through the same point of contact. The amount of the refund will be determined by the ticket restrictions. You can obtain a refund on both refundable and non-refundable tickets if you cancel your tickets within the <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/air-canada-airlines-refund-policy.aspx">Air Canada cancellation</a> period of 24 hours. </p>

